==English==
===Verb===
{{en-verb|pronate|pronates|pronated|pronating}}
#{{transitive}} to [[turn]] or [[rotate]] one’s [[hand]] so that the [[palm]] faces down or back.  To twist the foot so that if walking the weight would be borne on the inner edge of the foot.
#{{intransitive}} to become pronated

